<font face="times new roman" >
          <h4>CLINICAL PSYCHOLOGY </h4>
          <p>Involves diagnosing and treating mental illnesses and disorders. Clinical psychologists work in hospitals, clinics, and private practice.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
          <img src="social psychology.jpg">
          <h4>SOCIAL PSYCHOLOGY</h4>
          <p>Studies how people think, feel, and behave in social situations. Topics include group behavior, social interactions, and nonverbal communication. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <img src="developmental psychology.jpg">
          <h4>DEVELOPMENTAL PSYCHOLOGY</h4>
          <p>Studies how people grow and adapt from conception to death. Developmental psychologists can help people reach their full potential.</p></font> 
        </div>
